{"tid":2249230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"名帥：美斯自己能做很多事 C朗需要所有人的幫助","createTime":"2020-10-19T08:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T00:32:00.000Z","uid":7439,"like":14,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"20086d63caaca3cb215f3d04fab9e1f93512bec9","tid":2249230,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:04:48.000Z","msg":"歐冠本週就將開戰，名帥盧西斯古(Mircea Lucescu)率領的基輔戴拿模與尤文和巴薩分在了同一小組，首輪他們將對陣斑馬軍團。在接受歐足聯官網採訪時，盧塞斯庫也談到了梅西和C羅的技術特點。<br />\n<br />\n  &ldquo;我和他們交手過很多次，但我手下的這批球員們並沒有。不久之後他們就會遇到這兩人了，我得跟球員們解析他們的踢法是怎麼樣的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;梅西是一名相對矮小的球員，他在狹小空間裡的能力非同凡響，這是因為他的加速能力、自信心、盤帶技巧以及所有這些東西。C羅是一名不同類型的球員，因為他是如此喜歡進球，他需要更大一些的空間。他需要所有人的幫助，他的隊友們的幫助。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;<span class=\"red\">梅西可以靠他自己來做很多事情。C羅在禁區內或者是門前20米區域可以有一己之力，但他會努力去利用其他人創造出來的空間，然後他來攻門得分。</span>就是這樣：他們風格不同，但都是真的非常強的球員。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"7b5b2c06ddfadb0606c46b43134f226298bb2e92","tid":2249230,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"活著何求7日冇出post了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb10a448c9d070b6f801c6a52bc89557af28a08","tid":2249230,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/216/w650h366/20201019/4960-kaqzmiw7522924.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F216%2Fw650h366%2F20201019%2F4960-kaqzmiw7522924.png&h=960f87c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴薩最新的降薪要求遭到了球員的拒絕，巴薩更衣室拒絕高層降薪30%的提議，他們準備以傳真的方式通告俱樂部高層。不過加泰羅尼亞電台透露，巴薩更衣室並非鐵板一塊，有三位球員就沒有在拒絕降薪的聯名信上簽名。<br />\n<br />\n  不過加泰電台報導，德容、朗格萊和特爾施特根沒有在這份傳真上簽名，原因不詳。特爾施特根正和俱樂部談續約，或許他不想因此影響談判。目前還不清楚3名球員不簽名，對球員的抵抗力度是否有影響。不過，球隊的四大隊長梅西、布斯克茨、皮克和羅伯托都已經簽名。"},{"pid":"743a36dbcbac157f2d918c1d6871f9530363e0d0","tid":2249230,"uid":58811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b5b2c06ddfadb0606c46b43134f226298bb2e92","tid":2249230,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"活著何求7日冇出post了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"我們懷念牠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777483d1a88455f314699db1c287ffc9b5e17b2b","tid":2249230,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"活sir似去咗泰國做抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e290147327a2607eb31ce2e40f3862a642d3fa82","tid":2249230,"uid":343419,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:10:24.000Z","msg":"美斯=斑<br />\n牙朗=柱間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea8d4e82a1ea5a1393bdf3862dd31f1616b7635","tid":2249230,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"留意到自從雞姦中咗武肺，活蛇就再無出現"},{"pid":"e2bf2547c3a29abdb842cbe342ffbd80e991364c","tid":2249230,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eea8d4e82a1ea5a1393bdf3862dd31f1616b7635","tid":2249230,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"留意到自從雞姦中咗武肺，活蛇就再無出現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226f9b274755fff4c393b05a4c419f865976ed1b","tid":2249230,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eea8d4e82a1ea5a1393bdf3862dd31f1616b7635","tid":2249230,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"留意到自從雞姦中咗武肺，活蛇就再無出現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真人？"},{"pid":"29acad977fb1f3c0d52e0cf4b9c1bb5ea73fb862","tid":2249230,"uid":7043,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"r